.card
    .card-header.pb-0
        +card-header('Solid border style', '','', 'Use the', '.default-border-style-*.mega-inline-*', 'you can archive this style.')
    .card-body.megaoptions-border-space-sm.checkbox-checked
        form.mega-inline.default-border-style
            .row.flex-column
                .col-12
                    .card
                        .p-20
                            .form-check
                                input#flexRadioDefault1.form-check-input(type='radio' name='flexRadioDefault')
                                label.form-check-label(for='flexRadioDefault1') 
                                    span.flex-grow-1
                                        span.d-flex.list-behavior-1
                                            span.flex-shrink-0
                                                img.tab-img.img-fluid(src="../assets/images/blog/img.png" alt="home") 
                                            span.flex-grow-1    
                                                span.mb-0
                                                    | We provide end to end digital solutions, right from designing your website/application development: Domain, Web Hosting, Email Hosting Registration.
                .col-12
                    .card
                        .p-20
                            .form-check
                                input#flexRadioDefault2.form-check-input(type='radio' name='flexRadioDefault' checked='')
                                label.form-check-label(for='flexRadioDefault2')
                                    span.flex-grow-1
                                        span.d-flex.list-behavior-1
                                            span.flex-shrink-0 
                                                img.tab-img.img-fluid(src="../assets/images/blog/blog.jpg" alt="home")
                                            span.flex-grow-1
                                                span.mb-0
                                                    | When someone visits your homepage, your design should inspire them to stay. Therefore, your value proposition should be established on the homepage for visitors.
    .card-footer.text-end
        button.btn.btn-primary.m-r-15(type='submit') Submit
        button.btn.bg-light(type='submit') Cancel